---
title: Creamy Stracciatella Cheese and Tomato Sandwich with Roasted Potato Wedges
description: We've taken the classic Italian antipasto and made it a meal for two! Toast ciabatta buns are brushed with garlic oil and topped with creamy stracciatella, juicy tomatoes and fresh basil. A final drizzle of balsamic glaze and you're all set for date night!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-stracciatella-cheese-and-tomato-sandwich-24f50319.jpg
